reviewText: Despite numerous attempts to correct the problem, Amazon continues to leave this movie, Animal Kingdom-Bears, Wolves linked to the stars of the 1932 movie The Animal Kingdom.  They are not the same movie!!!!  Animal Kingdom-Bears, Wolves is about the 4 legged creatures, perhaps Smokey the Bear is the star.  The Animal Kingdom (1932) stars the 2 legged variety with the lovely cast led by Ann Harding and Myrna Loy.
